AN Inverclyde company has been nominated for an industry gong. Wedding firm up for award AN Inverclyde company has been nominated for an industry gong.Gryffe Weddings of Kilmacolm has been put forward as best wedding film supplier in the 10th Scottish Vows Awards just seven months after launching Britain's first video bridal magazine.Company bosses will learn their fate at &shy;Hilton Glasgow on &shy;November 22. 